---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/home/Hero.astro";
import heroImage from "../assets/hero.png";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Creando Sustain — Creando Futuronan"
  description="A school for building futures that actually last."
>
  <Hero
    headline="Creando Sustain (18–30)"
    sub="A school for building futures that actually last — where imagination meets survival skills."
    ctas={[
      { label: "Express interest", href: "#apply" },
      { label: "Intro session", href: "#intro" },
    ]}
    image={heroImage}
  />

  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 lg:py-14">
    <div class="prose prose-sm sm:prose lg:prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p>
        You’ll learn how to make a living <em>and</em> make a difference — grow your
        craft and your community. It’s not about chasing “success.” It’s about making
        futures that can hold us.
      </p>

      <h2 class="h2 mt-10">About the programme</h2>
      <p>
        An intensive <strong>8-session evening laboratory</strong> (2× per week)
        for young creatives. Develop a project prototype rooted in your reality,
        with mentorship and peer support.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>When:</strong> Tue & Thu evenings — 11 Nov to 6 Dec (in person)
        </li>
        <li><strong>Commitment:</strong> Full attendance required</li>
        <li><strong>Support:</strong> Stipend awarded upon completion</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10">Methodologies</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Contextual Design:</strong> Design from your own stories, culture,
        and environment.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Popular Education:</strong> Learning as a collective act of resistance.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Radical Data:</strong> Desire → Systems → Imagination → Making.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10" id="team">Team</h3>
      <p>
        Co-hosted by Radical Data, Plataforma Aruba, Metabolic Foundation,
        Counter/Narratives & Afaina de Jong. See <a href="/about#partners"
          >partners →</a>
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10">Location</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>RAA! (Residencia Artistico Aruba)</strong><br />Caya Betico
        Croes 110, Oranjestad, Aruba
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10">Language</h3>
      <p>Sessions in English, with support in Papiamento and Spanish.</p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10" id="intro">Open intro session</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Sat, 18 Oct — 11:00</strong> at <strong>RAA!</strong>. We’ll
        present the school’s vision and programme.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10" id="apply">How to apply</h3>
      <p>
        After the intro, submit a short motivation letter or video via WhatsApp: <a
          href="https://wa.me/2975689420"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">+297 568 9420</a
        >.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a
          href="#apply"
          class="btn-primary btn-md"
          style="background: var(--color-brand);">Express interest</a
        >
        <a href="#intro" class="btn-outline btn-md ml-2">Intro details</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
